  Scenario: a seeded assign_scenarios is consumed and the structural loop deposits a status complete work_done via emit_r
    Given a BC orchestrated under fabro with a seeded assign_scenarios message in its registered mailbox
    When the structural Implementer-to-Reviewer graph executes to completion
    Then the graph nodes run in order and emit_r is the sole in-graph node that emits work_done
